        <description>&lt;p&gt;```elixir
defmodule Hedwig.Handlers.Echo do
@moduledoc “””
A completely useless echo script.
This script simply echoes the same message back.
“””&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;@usage nil&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;use Hedwig.Handler&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;def handle_event(%Message{} = msg, opts) do
reply(msg, msg.body)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;end&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;def handle_event(_, opts), do: {:ok, opts}
end
```&lt;/p&gt;

